hands_on_practices.solution:
可进化性定义为 $E=\left(\frac{\sigma}{\mu}\right)^{2}$。对于对照组和处理组，它们的可进化性分别为 $E_{\text{control}}=\left(\frac{\sigma_{c}}{\mu_{c}}\right)^{2}$ 和 $E_{\text{treatment}}=\left(\frac{\sigma_{t}}{\mu_{t}}\right)^{2}$。所要求的比率为
$$
\frac{E_{\text{treatment}}}{E_{\text{control}}}
=\frac{\left(\frac{\sigma_{t}}{\mu_{t}}\right)^{2}}{\left(\frac{\sigma_{c}}{\mu_{c}}\right)^{2}}
=\left(\frac{\sigma_{t}}{\sigma_{c}}\right)^{2}\left(\frac{\mu_{c}}{\mu_{t}}\right)^{2}.
$$
代入给定值 $\sigma_{t}=0.95$，$\mu_{t}=4.85$，$\sigma_{c}=0.25$ 和 $\mu_{c}=5.10$，
$$
\frac{E_{\text{treatment}}}{E_{\text{control}}}
=\left(\frac{0.95}{0.25}\right)^{2}\left(\frac{5.10}{4.85}\right)^{2}
=(3.8)^{2}\left(1.0515\ldots\right)^{2}
\approx (14.44)(1.1057)
\approx 15.967.
$$
四舍五入至三位有效数字得到 $16.0$。
